{"video_id": "9RWXaUYmybY", "title": "2016-07-28 | SB 3.25.8 | HG Amitasana Dasa", "speaker": "HG Amitasana Dasa", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9RWXaUYmybY", "duration": 2051, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 2.0, "text": " Amen."}, {"start": 30.0, "end": 32.0, "text": " Amen."}, {"start": 60.0, "end": 62.0, "text": " Amen."}, {"start": 90.0, "end": 92.0, "text": " Amen."}, {"start": 120.0, "end": 122.0, "text": " Amen."}, {"start": 150.0, "end": 152.0, "text": " Amen."}, {"start": 180.0, "end": 182.0, "text": " Amen."}, {"start": 210.0, "end": 238.2, "text": " And here it is also mentioned, I have attained after many, many births, by and large in this material world, the living entities are in a conditioned stage, in darkness, overpowered by ignorance."}, {"start": 240.0, "end": 253.0, "text": " In the spiritual world, everyone is situated in their constitutional position, enlightened, in knowledge, serving the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 253.0, "end": 269.0, "text": " So in this material world, after many, many lifetimes, bahunam janmanam ante, labdhuva sudurlabham idam sahubham mama ante, which means after many, many births,"}, {"start": 269.0, "end": 270.0, "text": " ,"}, {"start": 270.0, "end": 287.0, "text": " labdhuva, we get human birth, and after many, many births, one comes to the understanding, vasudevam sarvam iti, and that is purely because of the mercy of a bona fide spiritual master,"}, {"start": 287.0, "end": 299.0, "text": " who brings us to light, and removes the darkness which is covering us."}, {"start": 299.0, "end": 313.0, "text": " So here Prabhupada mentions, the disciple or conditioned soul is put into this darkness region of ignorance, therefore is entangled in the material existence of sense gratification."}, {"start": 313.0, "end": 321.0, "text": " So Prabhupada also mentions there are two sides, one is the conditioned side, and the other side is life of freedom."}, {"start": 321.0, "end": 327.0, "text": " In conditioned life, we are in ignorance."}, {"start": 327.0, "end": 328.0, "text": " In conditioned life, we are in ignorance."}, {"start": 328.0, "end": 338.0, "text": " We are in ignorance, and entangled in the material existence of sense gratification."}, {"start": 338.0, "end": 346.0, "text": " We are in Kali Yuga, and in present time, we see Kali Yuga is in full force."}, {"start": 346.0, "end": 352.0, "text": " Sense gratification is very, very rampant."}, {"start": 352.0, "end": 356.0, "text": " In fact, for most of the people, that's the goal of life."}, {"start": 356.0, "end": 366.0, "text": " If we see today's newspapers, it's full of advertisements alluring people,"}, {"start": 366.0, "end": 370.0, "text": " with different kinds of allurements, different kinds of deals,"}, {"start": 370.0, "end": 382.0, "text": " different types of, so to say, propositions to gratify the senses."}, {"start": 382.0, "end": 384.0, "text": " Sometimes full, full pages of ads,"}, {"start": 384.0, "end": 394.0, "text": " like for example, there was one ad, billion day, billion day sale or something, billion sale."}, {"start": 394.0, "end": 400.0, "text": " Some four, five full pages ad, and different kinds of deals,"}, {"start": 400.0, "end": 406.0, "text": " how you can get a product at half the price, or discounted price, special price."}, {"start": 406.0, "end": 410.0, "text": " And there are different competitors who are competing,"}, {"start": 410.0, "end": 412.0, "text": " how to get customers, who are competing,"}, {"start": 412.0, "end": 416.0, "text": " how to get customers into their fold,"}, {"start": 416.0, "end": 420.0, "text": " how to increase their business."}, {"start": 420.0, "end": 424.0, "text": " And billions of dollars are being spent."}, {"start": 424.0, "end": 432.0, "text": " It's said that top 100 advertisers are spending close to about 15 billion dollars"}, {"start": 432.0, "end": 436.0, "text": " in different kinds of campaigns."}, {"start": 436.0, "end": 440.0, "text": " And I think I've shared this earlier,"}, {"start": 440.0, "end": 450.0, "text": " these days, marketing and sales experts, in fact they have degrees on that."}, {"start": 450.0, "end": 454.0, "text": " People go through two years, three years courses,"}, {"start": 454.0, "end": 460.0, "text": " how the mind of a customer can be pulled into buying the product."}, {"start": 460.0, "end": 464.0, "text": " And there are many, many intelligent people,"}, {"start": 464.0, "end": 468.0, "text": " people from IIMs and top colleges,"}, {"start": 468.0, "end": 472.0, "text": " who sit and strategize different campaigns."}, {"start": 472.0, "end": 478.0, "text": " In one sense, we don't even know how gullible we are,"}, {"start": 478.0, "end": 484.0, "text": " how helplessly, without our knowledge, we get influenced."}, {"start": 484.0, "end": 488.0, "text": " In other words, sometimes we use the word brainwashing,"}, {"start": 488.0, "end": 492.0, "text": " although we use it in a wrong context."}, {"start": 492.0, "end": 494.0, "text": " You know, when people come to spiritual life,"}, {"start": 494.0, "end": 496.0, "text": " come to ISKCON, and they hear philosophy,"}, {"start": 496.0, "end": 500.0, "text": " and then there is some transformation in their heart,"}, {"start": 500.0, "end": 502.0, "text": " so people say it's brainwashing."}, {"start": 502.0, "end": 504.0, "text": " But actually, it's a fact that"}, {"start": 504.0, "end": 508.0, "text": " the majority of people are getting brainwashed."}, {"start": 508.0, "end": 510.0, "text": " If you actually have to go by the word brainwashing,"}, {"start": 510.0, "end": 514.0, "text": " brainwashing means you're getting influenced helplessly."}, {"start": 514.0, "end": 518.0, "text": " You lose your original individuality."}, {"start": 520.0, "end": 522.0, "text": " So it's a very scary world,"}, {"start": 522.0, "end": 524.0, "text": " and these days,"}, {"start": 524.0, "end": 526.0, "text": " an average child,"}, {"start": 526.0, "end": 528.0, "text": " seven hours in a week,"}, {"start": 528.0, "end": 530.0, "text": " he spends in front of a television."}, {"start": 530.0, "end": 532.0, "text": " And different kinds of commercials,"}, {"start": 532.0, "end": 534.0, "text": " different kinds of advertising,"}, {"start": 534.0, "end": 536.0, "text": " what all is going on in his head,"}, {"start": 536.0, "end": 538.0, "text": " what all worldview he's forming"}, {"start": 538.0, "end": 540.0, "text": " based on those advertisements"}, {"start": 540.0, "end": 542.0, "text": " which people have strategized"}, {"start": 542.0, "end": 544.0, "text": " to influence our minds."}, {"start": 550.0, "end": 552.0, "text": " Krishna also says,"}, {"start": 552.0, "end": 554.0, "text": " those who are"}, {"start": 554.0, "end": 556.0, "text": " on this path,"}, {"start": 556.0, "end": 558.0, "text": " their mind,"}, {"start": 558.0, "end": 560.0, "text": " their intelligence,"}, {"start": 560.0, "end": 562.0, "text": " is resolute."}, {"start": 562.0, "end": 564.0, "text": " So in one sense,"}, {"start": 564.0, "end": 566.0, "text": " it's a very scary world,"}, {"start": 566.0, "end": 568.0, "text": " it's a very precarious condition."}, {"start": 568.0, "end": 570.0, "text": " We are very very fortunate,"}, {"start": 570.0, "end": 572.0, "text": " we are very very blessed"}, {"start": 572.0, "end": 574.0, "text": " that we are in a very very,"}, {"start": 574.0, "end": 576.0, "text": " so to say, protected environment."}, {"start": 576.0, "end": 578.0, "text": " We don't even have an option"}, {"start": 578.0, "end": 580.0, "text": " to watch a television."}, {"start": 580.0, "end": 582.0, "text": " Otherwise,"}, {"start": 582.0, "end": 584.0, "text": " it's very alluring,"}, {"start": 584.0, "end": 586.0, "text": " it's very very tempting."}, {"start": 586.0, "end": 588.0, "text": " You may even go for"}, {"start": 588.0, "end": 590.0, "text": " seeing something like news or something,"}, {"start": 590.0, "end": 592.0, "text": " but then you get pulled into so many things."}, {"start": 592.0, "end": 594.0, "text": " And a lot of people,"}, {"start": 594.0, "end": 596.0, "text": " even so-called Karmis say"}, {"start": 596.0, "end": 598.0, "text": " that it is the biggest distraction"}, {"start": 598.0, "end": 600.0, "text": " in the household these days."}, {"start": 600.0, "end": 602.0, "text": " An average parent spends"}, {"start": 602.0, "end": 604.0, "text": " about three and a half minutes"}, {"start": 604.0, "end": 606.0, "text": " of meaningful conversation time"}, {"start": 606.0, "end": 608.0, "text": " with his child in a week,"}, {"start": 608.0, "end": 610.0, "text": " vis-a-vis 27 hours"}, {"start": 610.0, "end": 612.0, "text": " in front of television."}, {"start": 612.0, "end": 614.0, "text": " So already we have,"}, {"start": 614.0, "end": 616.0, "text": " conditioned soul has"}, {"start": 616.0, "end": 618.0, "text": " uncontrolled senses,"}, {"start": 618.0, "end": 620.0, "text": " uncontrolled mind."}, {"start": 620.0, "end": 622.0, "text": " Krishna says,"}, {"start": 622.0, "end": 624.0, "text": " mind if it is uncontrolled"}, {"start": 624.0, "end": 626.0, "text": " is a worst enemy."}, {"start": 626.0, "end": 628.0, "text": " And a conditioned soul"}, {"start": 628.0, "end": 630.0, "text": " has a natural inclination"}, {"start": 630.0, "end": 632.0, "text": " to gratify the senses,"}, {"start": 632.0, "end": 634.0, "text": " enjoy the senses."}, {"start": 634.0, "end": 636.0, "text": " Krishna is saying"}, {"start": 636.0, "end": 638.0, "text": " from the very beginning,"}, {"start": 638.0, "end": 640.0, "text": " regulate the senses"}, {"start": 640.0, "end": 642.0, "text": " and slay this destroyer"}, {"start": 642.0, "end": 644.0, "text": " and on the other side"}, {"start": 644.0, "end": 646.0, "text": " we have a world where"}, {"start": 646.0, "end": 648.0, "text": " there are unlimited opportunities"}, {"start": 648.0, "end": 650.0, "text": " to gratify the senses."}, {"start": 652.0, "end": 654.0, "text": " To let the mind go"}, {"start": 654.0, "end": 656.0, "text": " completely loose."}, {"start": 658.0, "end": 660.0, "text": " So in that sense,"}, {"start": 660.0, "end": 662.0, "text": " it's a great fortune"}, {"start": 662.0, "end": 664.0, "text": " that we are practicing"}, {"start": 664.0, "end": 666.0, "text": " spiritual life where"}, {"start": 666.0, "end": 668.0, "text": " five hours, six hours,"}, {"start": 668.0, "end": 670.0, "text": " especially the sadhana time,"}, {"start": 670.0, "end": 672.0, "text": " we can completely focus"}, {"start": 672.0, "end": 674.0, "text": " in remembering the lord,"}, {"start": 674.0, "end": 676.0, "text": " thinking about the lord,"}, {"start": 676.0, "end": 678.0, "text": " chanting his holy name,"}, {"start": 678.0, "end": 680.0, "text": " doing kirtans,"}, {"start": 680.0, "end": 682.0, "text": " hearing about him,"}, {"start": 682.0, "end": 684.0, "text": " bhagavatam class,"}, {"start": 684.0, "end": 686.0, "text": " which is not at all possible"}, {"start": 686.0, "end": 688.0, "text": " in the outside world."}, {"start": 688.0, "end": 690.0, "text": " At best many people are able"}, {"start": 690.0, "end": 692.0, "text": " to just finish their rounds"}, {"start": 692.0, "end": 694.0, "text": " if they are really genuine"}, {"start": 694.0, "end": 696.0, "text": " and serious in spirituality."}, {"start": 696.0, "end": 698.0, "text": " Sometimes people start off"}, {"start": 698.0, "end": 700.0, "text": " with 16 rounds"}, {"start": 700.0, "end": 702.0, "text": " but because of circumstances"}, {"start": 702.0, "end": 704.0, "text": " so many commitments,"}, {"start": 704.0, "end": 706.0, "text": " so many responsibilities,"}, {"start": 706.0, "end": 708.0, "text": " they gradually come down"}, {"start": 708.0, "end": 710.0, "text": " eight rounds, four rounds."}, {"start": 712.0, "end": 714.0, "text": " So this is the life"}, {"start": 714.0, "end": 716.0, "text": " of ignorance,"}, {"start": 716.0, "end": 718.0, "text": " life of bondage,"}, {"start": 718.0, "end": 720.0, "text": " life, conditioned life"}, {"start": 720.0, "end": 722.0, "text": " full of gratification of senses."}, {"start": 722.0, "end": 724.0, "text": " So Prabhupada says"}, {"start": 724.0, "end": 726.0, "text": " the spiritual master"}, {"start": 726.0, "end": 728.0, "text": " is therefore worshipped"}, {"start": 728.0, "end": 730.0, "text": " as one who delivers the disciple"}, {"start": 730.0, "end": 732.0, "text": " to the other side"}, {"start": 732.0, "end": 734.0, "text": " with the light of knowledge."}, {"start": 734.0, "end": 736.0, "text": " The word paragram,"}, {"start": 736.0, "end": 738.0, "text": " para also means uspar."}, {"start": 738.0, "end": 740.0, "text": " I think it comes from that word"}, {"start": 740.0, "end": 742.0, "text": " uspar, uspar leke jana."}, {"start": 742.0, "end": 744.0, "text": " Uspar means the other side."}, {"start": 744.0, "end": 746.0, "text": " Gam means to go,"}, {"start": 746.0, "end": 748.0, "text": " to take."}, {"start": 748.0, "end": 750.0, "text": " The word paragam is very significant."}, {"start": 750.0, "end": 752.0, "text": " Paragram refers to one"}, {"start": 752.0, "end": 754.0, "text": " who can take the disciple"}, {"start": 754.0, "end": 756.0, "text": " to the other side."}, {"start": 756.0, "end": 758.0, "text": " So what spiritual master does"}, {"start": 758.0, "end": 760.0, "text": " is conditioned soul"}, {"start": 760.0, "end": 762.0, "text": " to the other side"}, {"start": 762.0, "end": 764.0, "text": " completely engrossed"}, {"start": 764.0, "end": 766.0, "text": " and gratifying the senses,"}, {"start": 766.0, "end": 768.0, "text": " completely ignorant of"}, {"start": 768.0, "end": 770.0, "text": " the purpose of human form of life"}, {"start": 770.0, "end": 772.0, "text": " pulls that disciple"}, {"start": 772.0, "end": 774.0, "text": " and takes him"}, {"start": 774.0, "end": 776.0, "text": " to the other side"}, {"start": 776.0, "end": 778.0, "text": " which is"}, {"start": 778.0, "end": 780.0, "text": " other side of light,"}, {"start": 780.0, "end": 782.0, "text": " other side of enlightenment,"}, {"start": 782.0, "end": 784.0, "text": " other side of knowledge."}, {"start": 788.0, "end": 790.0, "text": " Now it is very important for us"}, {"start": 790.0, "end": 792.0, "text": " to understand"}, {"start": 792.0, "end": 794.0, "text": " what process we are following,"}, {"start": 794.0, "end": 796.0, "text": " what process Shri Prabhupada"}, {"start": 796.0, "end": 798.0, "text": " has given us."}, {"start": 798.0, "end": 800.0, "text": " Even in the Bhagavad Gita"}, {"start": 800.0, "end": 802.0, "text": " Krishna talks about Ashtanga Yoga"}, {"start": 802.0, "end": 804.0, "text": " which"}, {"start": 804.0, "end": 806.0, "text": " yama, niyama, asana,"}, {"start": 806.0, "end": 808.0, "text": " control of mind,"}, {"start": 808.0, "end": 810.0, "text": " control of senses,"}, {"start": 810.0, "end": 812.0, "text": " sitting in rigid posture."}, {"start": 812.0, "end": 814.0, "text": " He tells Arjuna"}, {"start": 814.0, "end": 816.0, "text": " and Arjuna as we know"}, {"start": 816.0, "end": 818.0, "text": " he expresses his inability"}, {"start": 818.0, "end": 820.0, "text": " to follow that process."}, {"start": 820.0, "end": 822.0, "text": " And that was 5000 years back."}, {"start": 826.0, "end": 828.0, "text": " So"}, {"start": 828.0, "end": 830.0, "text": " mind is very turbulent,"}, {"start": 830.0, "end": 832.0, "text": " mind is very restless"}, {"start": 832.0, "end": 834.0, "text": " and Krishna himself is recommending"}, {"start": 834.0, "end": 836.0, "text": " to control the mind"}, {"start": 836.0, "end": 838.0, "text": " you go to secluded place"}, {"start": 838.0, "end": 840.0, "text": " sit in a rigid posture"}, {"start": 840.0, "end": 842.0, "text": " yama, niyama, pranayama,"}, {"start": 842.0, "end": 844.0, "text": " asana, dharana"}, {"start": 844.0, "end": 846.0, "text": " and finally one will come to a sage"}, {"start": 846.0, "end": 848.0, "text": " where dhyana"}, {"start": 848.0, "end": 850.0, "text": " one will be able to focus"}, {"start": 850.0, "end": 852.0, "text": " his mind,"}, {"start": 852.0, "end": 854.0, "text": " withdraw from the senses"}, {"start": 854.0, "end": 856.0, "text": " and focus his mind on the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 860.0, "end": 862.0, "text": " It could be after many many lifetimes."}, {"start": 862.0, "end": 864.0, "text": " In Satya Yuga"}, {"start": 864.0, "end": 866.0, "text": " it used to be after many many thousands of years."}, {"start": 866.0, "end": 868.0, "text": " Lifespan was longer."}, {"start": 870.0, "end": 872.0, "text": " So"}, {"start": 872.0, "end": 874.0, "text": " out of causeless mercy"}, {"start": 874.0, "end": 876.0, "text": " what in Kali Yuga we are getting"}, {"start": 876.0, "end": 878.0, "text": " the process by Shri Prabhupada"}, {"start": 878.0, "end": 880.0, "text": " or Acharyas are giving us"}, {"start": 880.0, "end": 882.0, "text": " the Bhakti Yoga process"}, {"start": 882.0, "end": 884.0, "text": " where instead of following"}, {"start": 884.0, "end": 886.0, "text": " all the strict rules and regulations"}, {"start": 888.0, "end": 890.0, "text": " we start with the end."}, {"start": 890.0, "end": 892.0, "text": " End is what"}, {"start": 892.0, "end": 894.0, "text": " even though our mind"}, {"start": 894.0, "end": 896.0, "text": " and senses are completely untamed"}, {"start": 896.0, "end": 898.0, "text": " we are in a conditioned stage"}, {"start": 898.0, "end": 900.0, "text": " we are in ignorance"}, {"start": 900.0, "end": 902.0, "text": " we start with the end"}, {"start": 902.0, "end": 904.0, "text": " that is to serve the Supreme Lord"}, {"start": 904.0, "end": 908.0, "text": " which is our constitutional position"}, {"start": 908.0, "end": 910.0, "text": " Jivera Swaroopahoe"}, {"start": 910.0, "end": 912.0, "text": " Nityera Krishna Das"}, {"start": 912.0, "end": 914.0, "text": " So without even"}, {"start": 914.0, "end": 916.0, "text": " bothering to control"}, {"start": 916.0, "end": 918.0, "text": " our mind and senses"}, {"start": 918.0, "end": 920.0, "text": " not that sometimes people say"}, {"start": 920.0, "end": 922.0, "text": " should I give up this, should I give up that"}, {"start": 922.0, "end": 924.0, "text": " should I give up all non-veg"}, {"start": 924.0, "end": 926.0, "text": " should I give up smoking everything"}, {"start": 926.0, "end": 928.0, "text": " and then I can chant Hare Krishna Maha Mantra"}, {"start": 928.0, "end": 930.0, "text": " Generally we say no"}, {"start": 930.0, "end": 932.0, "text": " you can have a desire to give up"}, {"start": 932.0, "end": 934.0, "text": " Hare Krishna Mantra"}, {"start": 934.0, "end": 936.0, "text": " One day it may so happen that"}, {"start": 936.0, "end": 938.0, "text": " if you are continuing to chant"}, {"start": 938.0, "end": 940.0, "text": " you automatically will develop a distaste"}, {"start": 940.0, "end": 942.0, "text": " and a desire to give it up"}, {"start": 942.0, "end": 944.0, "text": " That's our process"}, {"start": 944.0, "end": 946.0, "text": " Same is the case with Bhakti Yoga"}, {"start": 946.0, "end": 948.0, "text": " It is not that we are all"}, {"start": 948.0, "end": 950.0, "text": " great Yogis in terms of"}, {"start": 950.0, "end": 952.0, "text": " controlling the mind, controlling the senses"}, {"start": 952.0, "end": 954.0, "text": " still we see our senses are"}, {"start": 954.0, "end": 956.0, "text": " many times they overpower us"}, {"start": 958.0, "end": 960.0, "text": " We still have inclination to gratify"}, {"start": 960.0, "end": 962.0, "text": " our senses"}, {"start": 962.0, "end": 964.0, "text": " Still our mind is"}, {"start": 964.0, "end": 966.0, "text": " we can understand"}, {"start": 966.0, "end": 968.0, "text": " it is not fully in our control"}, {"start": 968.0, "end": 970.0, "text": " it is untamed"}, {"start": 970.0, "end": 972.0, "text": " Again it is not a binary logic"}, {"start": 972.0, "end": 974.0, "text": " zero or one"}, {"start": 974.0, "end": 976.0, "text": " So we start with the end"}, {"start": 976.0, "end": 978.0, "text": " that is to serve the Supreme Lord"}, {"start": 982.0, "end": 984.0, "text": " We start serving"}, {"start": 984.0, "end": 986.0, "text": " the master of the senses"}, {"start": 986.0, "end": 988.0, "text": " the Lord with our senses"}, {"start": 988.0, "end": 990.0, "text": " and gradually what happens"}, {"start": 990.0, "end": 992.0, "text": " is our desire to serve"}, {"start": 992.0, "end": 994.0, "text": " our senses"}, {"start": 996.0, "end": 998.0, "text": " desire to gratify the senses"}, {"start": 998.0, "end": 1000.0, "text": " automatically becomes"}, {"start": 1000.0, "end": 1002.0, "text": " distasteful"}, {"start": 1002.0, "end": 1004.0, "text": " we lose taste for it"}, {"start": 1004.0, "end": 1006.0, "text": " we develop a higher taste"}, {"start": 1006.0, "end": 1008.0, "text": " and"}, {"start": 1008.0, "end": 1010.0, "text": " it automatically is pushed out"}, {"start": 1010.0, "end": 1012.0, "text": " of the system"}, {"start": 1014.0, "end": 1016.0, "text": " Otherwise the other process involves"}, {"start": 1018.0, "end": 1020.0, "text": " strict control of the senses"}, {"start": 1020.0, "end": 1022.0, "text": " strict control of the mind then Dhyana"}, {"start": 1022.0, "end": 1024.0, "text": " and finally one reaches a stage"}, {"start": 1024.0, "end": 1026.0, "text": " where one gets linked"}, {"start": 1026.0, "end": 1028.0, "text": " or connected with the Supreme Lord"}, {"start": 1028.0, "end": 1030.0, "text": " again link means what"}, {"start": 1030.0, "end": 1032.0, "text": " Jivera Swaroopa Hoey Nittyarak"}, {"start": 1032.0, "end": 1034.0, "text": " and then you have to serve"}, {"start": 1034.0, "end": 1036.0, "text": " It is not that"}, {"start": 1036.0, "end": 1038.0, "text": " just get linked"}, {"start": 1038.0, "end": 1040.0, "text": " understanding that this is"}, {"start": 1040.0, "end": 1042.0, "text": " my constitutional position"}, {"start": 1042.0, "end": 1044.0, "text": " I am servant of Supreme Lord"}, {"start": 1044.0, "end": 1046.0, "text": " ultimately we have to serve"}, {"start": 1046.0, "end": 1048.0, "text": " and we are very fortunate"}, {"start": 1048.0, "end": 1050.0, "text": " very blessed"}, {"start": 1050.0, "end": 1067.0, "text": " We are starting with the end, serving the Supreme Lord, which is our constitutional position, and all the lower forms of service automatically gets, so to say, eliminated from our life, gradually."}, {"start": 1067.0, "end": 1073.0, "text": " And that is what purification is all about."}, {"start": 1073.0, "end": 1088.0, "text": " So, in Vedic times, people, knowing that we have a natural desire for gratifying our senses, people naturally would, knowing that ultimate goal of life is to purify the mind, purify the senses,"}, {"start": 1088.0, "end": 1101.0, "text": " the whole life was so organized, you know, in one sense, if you could say, the philosophy of life was simple living, high thinking."}, {"start": 1101.0, "end": 1103.0, "text": " Yes, we need to eat something."}, {"start": 1103.0, "end": 1105.0, "text": " To maintain this body."}, {"start": 1105.0, "end": 1111.0, "text": " There is a difference between eat to live, and live to eat."}, {"start": 1111.0, "end": 1116.0, "text": " Yes, we cannot completely give up eating."}, {"start": 1116.0, "end": 1123.0, "text": " And Krishna also does not forbid that you should not eat, you should eat only some bland food, without any salt."}, {"start": 1123.0, "end": 1128.0, "text": " Yajna shishtasana santo mucyante sarvakil bishay."}, {"start": 1128.0, "end": 1132.0, "text": " We can eat, we can offer to the Lord, purify, sanctify the foodstuff."}, {"start": 1132.0, "end": 1133.0, "text": " And we can eat."}, {"start": 1133.0, "end": 1135.0, "text": " And eat the remnants as prasadam."}, {"start": 1135.0, "end": 1143.0, "text": " So, the life was so organized, simple living, high thinking."}, {"start": 1143.0, "end": 1149.0, "text": " I was talking to someone on this line, in one of the sessions."}, {"start": 1149.0, "end": 1157.0, "text": " So, then I asked them, in Vedic times, life was simple living, high thinking."}, {"start": 1157.0, "end": 1161.0, "text": " What do you feel in present time, our life is, or people in general?"}, {"start": 1161.0, "end": 1162.0, "text": " What kind of philosophy are we?"}, {"start": 1162.0, "end": 1166.0, "text": " What kind of philosophy are we practicing?"}, {"start": 1166.0, "end": 1169.0, "text": " So, different people gave different answers."}, {"start": 1169.0, "end": 1172.0, "text": " One answer was quite interesting."}, {"start": 1172.0, "end": 1179.0, "text": " So, one person said, simply living, no thinking."}, {"start": 1179.0, "end": 1182.0, "text": " Simple living, high thinking."}, {"start": 1182.0, "end": 1184.0, "text": " Present time, it's simply living."}, {"start": 1184.0, "end": 1190.0, "text": " Actually, in one sense, without this higher purpose in life, it's simply living."}, {"start": 1190.0, "end": 1193.0, "text": " So, a person is living while being a person."}, {"start": 1193.0, "end": 1197.0, "text": " A person lives while being a person."}, {"start": 1197.0, "end": 1201.0, "text": " So, the ultimate goal is to live your life, and to live also."}, {"start": 1201.0, "end": 1203.0, "text": " I'd like to give some examples of that."}, {"start": 1203.0, "end": 1206.0, "text": " There is a person sitting next to you, and it's a long journey."}, {"start": 1206.0, "end": 1215.0, "text": " Sometimes it so happens, in the journey, we strike a conversation with the person sitting next to us, or in the same compartment."}, {"start": 1215.0, "end": 1216.0, "text": " So, you meet a person and then,"}, {"start": 1216.0, "end": 1217.0, "text": " you meet a person and then,"}, {"start": 1217.0, "end": 1218.0, "text": " you meet a person and then,"}, {"start": 1218.0, "end": 1223.62, "text": " You ask him, where are you going?"}, {"start": 1226.92, "end": 1234.1, "text": " So he looks at you, looks completely blanked out, and says, I don't know."}, {"start": 1237.14, "end": 1239.7, "text": " He says, where did you board the train?"}, {"start": 1242.34, "end": 1247.48, "text": " He looks and says, I don't know."}, {"start": 1248.0, "end": 1253.26, "text": " He says, where are you heading? Where will you get down?"}, {"start": 1254.3, "end": 1257.24, "text": " Again, thinks for a while and says, I don't know."}, {"start": 1261.18, "end": 1262.28, "text": " Why are you traveling?"}, {"start": 1265.0, "end": 1266.72, "text": " Looks, I don't know."}, {"start": 1267.86, "end": 1271.92, "text": " If you come across such a person who gives this kind of answer, what will you think about that person?"}, {"start": 1273.76, "end": 1274.64, "text": " I don't know."}, {"start": 1278.0, "end": 1279.64, "text": " What will you think about that person?"}, {"start": 1280.62, "end": 1281.5, "text": " He is mad."}, {"start": 1283.72, "end": 1285.1, "text": " Don't know where he got up."}, {"start": 1285.22, "end": 1286.58, "text": " Don't know where he is traveling."}, {"start": 1286.72, "end": 1288.02, "text": " Don't know where he is going to get down."}, {"start": 1288.78, "end": 1290.12, "text": " Why he is traveling, he doesn't know."}, {"start": 1290.4, "end": 1295.2, "text": " Actually, in one sense, this is applicable to all of us in the material world,"}, {"start": 1295.62, "end": 1298.92, "text": " who are in conditioned stage."}, {"start": 1300.78, "end": 1304.38, "text": " Where we boarded the train, in a sense, when we came in this world,"}, {"start": 1305.18, "end": 1305.8, "text": " where were we?"}, {"start": 1305.86, "end": 1306.7, "text": " Where we boarded?"}, {"start": 1308.0, "end": 1310.0, "text": " We don't know."}, {"start": 1313.0, "end": 1315.0, "text": " Where we are going to get down, we don't know."}, {"start": 1315.5, "end": 1317.5, "text": " What happens after death, we don't know."}, {"start": 1317.5, "end": 1319.5, "text": " Why we are traveling?"}, {"start": 1319.5, "end": 1321.5, "text": " Simply traveling."}, {"start": 1321.5, "end": 1323.5, "text": " Simply living."}, {"start": 1325.5, "end": 1327.5, "text": " So in that sense, there is some kind of a madness."}, {"start": 1327.5, "end": 1329.5, "text": " Pramatta."}, {"start": 1329.5, "end": 1331.5, "text": " Nunam pramatta kurute vikarma."}, {"start": 1331.5, "end": 1333.5, "text": " Pramatta, this is madness."}, {"start": 1333.5, "end": 1335.5, "text": " Again, this madness we don't realize unless"}, {"start": 1335.5, "end": 1337.5, "text": " we come to life."}, {"start": 1338.0, "end": 1340.0, "text": " We don't realize."}, {"start": 1343.0, "end": 1345.0, "text": " Big big intellectuals, big big intelligent,"}, {"start": 1345.0, "end": 1347.0, "text": " it doesn't strike them,"}, {"start": 1347.0, "end": 1349.0, "text": " where were we before birth?"}, {"start": 1351.0, "end": 1353.0, "text": " What happens to us after death?"}, {"start": 1353.0, "end": 1358.0, "text": " These questions are, so to say, completely not ignored."}, {"start": 1358.0, "end": 1360.0, "text": " For many people, it is irrelevant."}, {"start": 1360.0, "end": 1362.0, "text": " It's not irrelevant for a person who is traveling,"}, {"start": 1362.0, "end": 1364.0, "text": " where he has to get down,"}, {"start": 1364.0, "end": 1366.0, "text": " what happens to him after he gets down, it's not irrelevant."}, {"start": 1366.0, "end": 1368.0, "text": " Where he boarded the train,"}, {"start": 1368.0, "end": 1369.0, "text": " the train is not irrelevant."}, {"start": 1369.0, "end": 1371.0, "text": " Why he is traveling is not irrelevant."}, {"start": 1371.0, "end": 1373.0, "text": " There is a purpose for all travel."}, {"start": 1373.0, "end": 1375.0, "text": " Nobody travels purposely."}, {"start": 1375.0, "end": 1377.0, "text": " Only a madman travels purposely."}, {"start": 1377.0, "end": 1379.0, "text": " We are traveling in this world."}, {"start": 1379.0, "end": 1380.0, "text": " We are embarked on this journey."}, {"start": 1380.0, "end": 1382.0, "text": " This life is like a journey."}, {"start": 1382.0, "end": 1384.0, "text": " What is the purpose?"}, {"start": 1388.0, "end": 1390.0, "text": " So conditioned state means we are completely"}, {"start": 1390.0, "end": 1394.0, "text": " oblivious of these fundamental realities of life."}, {"start": 1394.0, "end": 1396.0, "text": " And we are not even bothered about it."}, {"start": 1396.0, "end": 1398.0, "text": " This is the meaning of Maya or illusion."}, {"start": 1398.0, "end": 1401.0, "text": " Tamasi ma jyotir gama."}, {"start": 1401.0, "end": 1403.0, "text": " We are in tamas, deep darkness."}, {"start": 1403.0, "end": 1405.0, "text": " These questions don't even strike us."}, {"start": 1405.0, "end": 1408.0, "text": " Forget about seeking answers to these questions."}, {"start": 1408.0, "end": 1411.0, "text": " Athato brahma jagat."}, {"start": 1411.0, "end": 1413.0, "text": " Now that you have got human form of life,"}, {"start": 1413.0, "end": 1414.0, "text": " try to inquire,"}, {"start": 1414.0, "end": 1416.0, "text": " Who am I?"}, {"start": 1416.0, "end": 1418.0, "text": " What is the purpose of my existence?"}, {"start": 1418.0, "end": 1424.0, "text": " So, in the Vedic times,"}, {"start": 1424.0, "end": 1426.0, "text": " people were automatically,"}, {"start": 1426.0, "end": 1427.0, "text": " because they were guided by the Vedas,"}, {"start": 1427.0, "end": 1430.0, "text": " because they were guided by well qualified brahmanas,"}, {"start": 1430.0, "end": 1432.0, "text": " kings who were administering the kingdom"}, {"start": 1432.0, "end": 1433.0, "text": " based on their guidance,"}, {"start": 1433.0, "end": 1437.0, "text": " the whole by and large was simple living."}, {"start": 1437.0, "end": 1439.0, "text": " People would keep their lives simple,"}, {"start": 1439.0, "end": 1441.0, "text": " bare necessities."}, {"start": 1441.0, "end": 1443.0, "text": " One time it happened,"}, {"start": 1443.0, "end": 1445.0, "text": " a person from the United States,"}, {"start": 1445.0, "end": 1446.0, "text": " they came to India and"}, {"start": 1446.0, "end": 1449.0, "text": " you know, he was looking out for a yogi."}, {"start": 1449.0, "end": 1454.0, "text": " And so he was going around"}, {"start": 1454.0, "end": 1456.0, "text": " asking people where to find a yogi."}, {"start": 1456.0, "end": 1459.0, "text": " So finally he was told about a yogi"}, {"start": 1459.0, "end": 1462.0, "text": " and he went looking for him,"}, {"start": 1462.0, "end": 1464.0, "text": " found his address,"}, {"start": 1464.0, "end": 1466.0, "text": " got his house,"}, {"start": 1466.0, "end": 1468.0, "text": " and then reached his place"}, {"start": 1468.0, "end": 1470.0, "text": " and rang the bell."}, {"start": 1470.0, "end": 1471.0, "text": " The door opened."}, {"start": 1471.0, "end": 1474.0, "text": " He was welcomed inside."}, {"start": 1474.0, "end": 1477.0, "text": " So he introduced himself"}, {"start": 1477.0, "end": 1479.0, "text": " and as soon as he entered the house,"}, {"start": 1479.0, "end": 1481.0, "text": " he saw the house is completely empty."}, {"start": 1481.0, "end": 1484.0, "text": " There is a bookshelf where all this Ramayana,"}, {"start": 1484.0, "end": 1485.0, "text": " Mahabharata,"}, {"start": 1485.0, "end": 1487.0, "text": " Granthas are there."}, {"start": 1487.0, "end": 1489.0, "text": " And there is one mat,"}, {"start": 1489.0, "end": 1490.0, "text": " straw mat on the floor"}, {"start": 1490.0, "end": 1496.0, "text": " and one lamp on the side."}, {"start": 1496.0, "end": 1498.0, "text": " So this person was quite surprised"}, {"start": 1498.0, "end": 1502.0, "text": " that there is no furniture in the house."}, {"start": 1502.0, "end": 1504.0, "text": " So he asked the yogiji,"}, {"start": 1504.0, "end": 1507.0, "text": " where is your furniture?"}, {"start": 1507.0, "end": 1509.0, "text": " This person asked."}, {"start": 1509.0, "end": 1511.0, "text": " So the yogi asked this man,"}, {"start": 1511.0, "end": 1512.0, "text": " a foreigner,"}, {"start": 1512.0, "end": 1513.0, "text": " he says,"}, {"start": 1513.0, "end": 1515.0, "text": " where is your furniture?"}, {"start": 1515.0, "end": 1517.0, "text": " He says,"}, {"start": 1517.0, "end": 1518.0, "text": " my furniture?"}, {"start": 1518.0, "end": 1520.0, "text": " I am a traveller."}, {"start": 1520.0, "end": 1522.0, "text": " So the yogi said,"}, {"start": 1522.0, "end": 1523.0, "text": " so am I."}, {"start": 1527.0, "end": 1528.0, "text": " So in other words,"}, {"start": 1528.0, "end": 1529.0, "text": " in the Vedic time,"}, {"start": 1529.0, "end": 1532.0, "text": " people were quite aware that this life is not"}, {"start": 1532.0, "end": 1534.0, "text": " just like a traveller."}, {"start": 1535.0, "end": 1536.0, "text": " He is moving,"}, {"start": 1536.0, "end": 1538.0, "text": " he knows that"}, {"start": 1538.0, "end": 1539.0, "text": " wherever he is staying,"}, {"start": 1539.0, "end": 1541.0, "text": " it is not his permanent place."}, {"start": 1543.0, "end": 1544.0, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 1545.0, "end": 1547.0, "text": " one day he has to move on."}, {"start": 1547.0, "end": 1552.0, "text": " Knowing that even if we are on a journey,"}, {"start": 1552.0, "end": 1554.0, "text": " we don't get totally attached to the compartment"}, {"start": 1554.0, "end": 1555.0, "text": " in which we are travelling,"}, {"start": 1555.0, "end": 1557.0, "text": " the seat we are seated in."}, {"start": 1557.0, "end": 1559.0, "text": " Journey is going to end,"}, {"start": 1559.0, "end": 1561.0, "text": " we have to disembark."}, {"start": 1563.0, "end": 1565.0, "text": " It is not meaningless for a person"}, {"start": 1565.0, "end": 1567.0, "text": " who is enlightened to be detached."}, {"start": 1569.0, "end": 1571.0, "text": " Automatic Jnana and Vairagya,"}, {"start": 1571.0, "end": 1573.0, "text": " they go hand in hand."}, {"start": 1573.0, "end": 1574.0, "text": " A person who is enlightened,"}, {"start": 1574.0, "end": 1575.0, "text": " who can see that"}, {"start": 1575.0, "end": 1577.0, "text": " this life is temporary,"}, {"start": 1581.0, "end": 1583.0, "text": " will automatically be detached."}, {"start": 1585.0, "end": 1586.0, "text": " Just like Pariksit Maharaj,"}, {"start": 1586.0, "end": 1587.0, "text": " he knew that"}, {"start": 1587.0, "end": 1589.0, "text": " when the time came,"}, {"start": 1589.0, "end": 1590.0, "text": " he didn't"}, {"start": 1590.0, "end": 1591.0, "text": " by hook or crook"}, {"start": 1591.0, "end": 1593.0, "text": " try to elongate his life,"}, {"start": 1594.0, "end": 1596.0, "text": " counter the curse"}, {"start": 1596.0, "end": 1598.0, "text": " which the Brahmana boy had given."}, {"start": 1599.0, "end": 1601.0, "text": " He simply accepted that"}, {"start": 1601.0, "end": 1603.0, "text": " and prepared himself"}, {"start": 1603.0, "end": 1605.0, "text": " and died a glorious death,"}, {"start": 1605.0, "end": 1606.0, "text": " remembering the Lord,"}, {"start": 1606.0, "end": 1607.0, "text": " hearing about the Lord."}, {"start": 1607.0, "end": 1608.0, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 1608.0, "end": 1609.0, "text": " that was the awareness"}, {"start": 1609.0, "end": 1610.0, "text": " which everyone had."}, {"start": 1610.0, "end": 1611.0, "text": " Ultimately,"}, {"start": 1611.0, "end": 1612.0, "text": " it is about"}, {"start": 1612.0, "end": 1613.0, "text": " realizing God,"}, {"start": 1613.0, "end": 1614.0, "text": " developing our relationship with Him,"}, {"start": 1614.0, "end": 1615.0, "text": " remembering Him,"}, {"start": 1615.0, "end": 1616.0, "text": " executing our worldly duties,"}, {"start": 1616.0, "end": 1617.0, "text": " and finally,"}, {"start": 1617.0, "end": 1618.0, "text": " Anta Narayana Smriti,"}, {"start": 1618.0, "end": 1619.0, "text": " how we can die"}, {"start": 1619.0, "end": 1620.0, "text": " remembering the Supreme Lord."}, {"start": 1620.0, "end": 1621.0, "text": " So,"}, {"start": 1621.0, "end": 1622.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1622.0, "end": 1623.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1623.0, "end": 1624.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1624.0, "end": 1625.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1625.0, "end": 1626.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1626.0, "end": 1627.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1627.0, "end": 1628.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1628.0, "end": 1629.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1629.0, "end": 1630.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1630.0, "end": 1631.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1631.0, "end": 1632.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1632.0, "end": 1633.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1633.0, "end": 1634.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1634.0, "end": 1635.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1635.0, "end": 1636.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1636.0, "end": 1637.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1637.0, "end": 1638.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1638.0, "end": 1639.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1639.0, "end": 1640.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1640.0, "end": 1641.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1641.0, "end": 1642.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1642.0, "end": 1643.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1643.0, "end": 1644.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1644.0, "end": 1645.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1645.0, "end": 1646.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1646.0, "end": 1647.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1647.0, "end": 1648.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1648.0, "end": 1649.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1649.0, "end": 1650.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1650.0, "end": 1651.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1651.0, "end": 1652.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1652.0, "end": 1653.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1653.0, "end": 1654.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1654.0, "end": 1655.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1655.0, "end": 1656.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1656.0, "end": 1657.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1657.0, "end": 1658.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1658.0, "end": 1659.0, "text": " all of you"}, {"start": 1659.0, "end": 1660.0, "text": " for watching this video."}, {"start": 1660.0, "end": 1661.0, "text": " I would like to thank"}, {"start": 1661.0, "end": 1671.44, "text": " stage of life because of ignorance we gratify our senses no doubt many times"}, {"start": 1671.44, "end": 1676.54, "text": " because of having acted for so many times in so many lifetimes we have got"}, {"start": 1676.54, "end": 1685.36, "text": " habituated but the root cause is ignorance today still we may gratify the"}, {"start": 1685.36, "end": 1688.54, "text": " senses it may not be because of ignorance we may realize that it is"}, {"start": 1688.54, "end": 1698.08, "text": " wrong but we are conditioned to act in that way root cause is ignorance because"}, {"start": 1698.08, "end": 1701.44, "text": " of ignorance we gratified the sense of thinking that that will give me"}, {"start": 1701.44, "end": 1708.04, "text": " happiness and we did that again and again again and again again and again"}, {"start": 1708.04, "end": 1713.3799999999999, "text": " again and again till it became a habit and today even after we have the"}, {"start": 1713.3799999999999, "end": 1716.3, "text": " knowledge that I should not be doing this I should not be still I am"}, {"start": 1716.3, "end": 1718.5, "text": " helplessly acting at times"}, {"start": 1718.54, "end": 1722.68, "text": " because of habits because of conditioning that's the meaning of"}, {"start": 1722.68, "end": 1727.96, "text": " conditioning you've got conditioned to act in a particular way so what we are"}, {"start": 1727.96, "end": 1731.98, "text": " doing as sadhakas we are breaking that conditioning we have different"}, {"start": 1731.98, "end": 1736.18, "text": " anarthas different habits wrong habits we are trying to break those"}, {"start": 1736.18, "end": 1743.68, "text": " habits by cultivating good habits so that's why Prabhupada says in"}, {"start": 1743.68, "end": 1747.8799999999999, "text": " spirituality we have to be patient we have to be determined we have to be"}, {"start": 1748.54, "end": 1753.52, "text": " realistic sometimes we realize in spite of me chanting in spite of my doing all"}, {"start": 1753.52, "end": 1756.1599999999999, "text": " the things why I am still getting attracted why still I am getting"}, {"start": 1757.72, "end": 1761.62, "text": " helplessly so to say forced to gratify my senses"}, {"start": 1763.36, "end": 1767.62, "text": " in fact this is a question which Arjuna also asked where Krishna says it is lust only"}, {"start": 1769.36, "end": 1774.76, "text": " so the root cause is ignorance we are simply suffering because of ignorance by"}, {"start": 1774.76, "end": 1778.52, "text": " the instruction of the spiritual master the darkness of ignorance is removed"}, {"start": 1778.54, "end": 1785.32, "text": " and thus the disciple is unable to go to the side of freedom"}, {"start": 1788.32, "end": 1792.52, "text": " in fact everyone is wanting freedom but they don't know what freedom is"}, {"start": 1793.36, "end": 1797.32, "text": " see how people with so enthusiasm we celebrate Independence Day"}, {"start": 1800.3799999999999, "end": 1807.1599999999999, "text": " even if you see typically on 15th August now this month we're going to have 15th August you'll see"}, {"start": 1808.54, "end": 1812.78, "text": " if you're going on the roads you'll see people with tricolors selling and people"}, {"start": 1812.78, "end": 1819.5, "text": " having it on their vehicles and you know celebrating Independence Day so as a"}, {"start": 1819.5, "end": 1821.74, "text": " conditioned soul we want independence we want freedom"}, {"start": 1825.76, "end": 1836.08, "text": " but a spiritual master actually takes us to the side of light and the side of freedom the real freedom"}, {"start": 1838.54, "end": 1844.54, "text": " It is stated in the Bhagavad Gita that after many many births one surrenders to the Supreme Personality of Godhead."}, {"start": 1844.54, "end": 1856.54, "text": " Similarly, if after many many births one is able to find a bona fide spiritual master and surrender to such a bona fide representative of Krishna, one can be taken to the side of light."}, {"start": 1856.54, "end": 1868.54, "text": " See, if we look how fortunate we are, after many many births we get human birth."}, {"start": 1868.54, "end": 1877.54, "text": " And we see in human life there are so many people who have no clue of even God."}, {"start": 1877.54, "end": 1883.54, "text": " That birth also is rare. Even human birth is rare."}, {"start": 1883.54, "end": 1886.54, "text": " And then on top of that,"}, {"start": 1886.54, "end": 1893.54, "text": " birth in Bharatvarsha, Dharma Bhoomi, that's even more rare."}, {"start": 1893.54, "end": 1899.54, "text": " And then even though in India all kinds of people are there."}, {"start": 1899.54, "end": 1904.54, "text": " Then some people are little pious. They may not be religious, they are pious."}, {"start": 1904.54, "end": 1908.54, "text": " They may be little God-fearing."}, {"start": 1908.54, "end": 1915.54, "text": " And then out of them a subset, a small set is religious."}, {"start": 1915.54, "end": 1916.54, "text": " They may,"}, {"start": 1916.54, "end": 1922.54, "text": " religious in the sense they may religiously go to the temple but it's more of a,"}, {"start": 1922.54, "end": 1927.54, "text": " to assist or to enable their gratification of senses."}, {"start": 1927.54, "end": 1934.54, "text": " Lord is used as a means to an end. The end is gratification of senses."}, {"start": 1934.54, "end": 1939.54, "text": " And out of such religious people there are people who are,"}, {"start": 1939.54, "end": 1942.54, "text": " you know, started worshipping Lord,"}, {"start": 1942.54, "end": 1945.54, "text": " glorifying the Lord."}, {"start": 1945.54, "end": 1947.54, "text": " And the initial part I told is,"}, {"start": 1947.54, "end": 1952.54, "text": " Karmakant is completely interested in gratification of senses."}, {"start": 1952.54, "end": 1954.54, "text": " So that way,"}, {"start": 1960.54, "end": 1965.54, "text": " We are one in the billions of souls who has come to Krishna,"}, {"start": 1965.54, "end": 1969.54, "text": " who has got a bona fide spiritual master."}, {"start": 1969.54, "end": 1972.54, "text": " We've got the process, if we follow,"}, {"start": 1972.54, "end": 1974.54, "text": " we can cross over this ocean of nascence,"}, {"start": 1974.54, "end": 1976.54, "text": " come to light."}, {"start": 1976.54, "end": 1982.54, "text": " Only thing which is left for us is to just diligently and sincerely follow."}, {"start": 1982.54, "end": 1986.54, "text": " Rest everything what is required to cross this ocean of nascence,"}, {"start": 1986.54, "end": 1992.54, "text": " to come to light is all provided."}, {"start": 1992.54, "end": 1995.54, "text": " So that way we should realize our good fortune."}, {"start": 1995.54, "end": 1999.54, "text": " And sometimes something which comes very easily,"}, {"start": 1999.54, "end": 2001.54, "text": " something which we receive so cheaply,"}, {"start": 2001.54, "end": 2003.54, "text": " we don't value."}, {"start": 2003.54, "end": 2006.54, "text": " And we can also come to the understanding,"}, {"start": 2006.54, "end": 2012.54, "text": " when we see somebody apparently happy, smiling,"}, {"start": 2012.54, "end": 2015.54, "text": " they say grass is greener the other side,"}, {"start": 2015.54, "end": 2020.54, "text": " we sometime may wonder what am I doing here."}, {"start": 2020.54, "end": 2022.54, "text": " So if we realize how fortunate we are,"}, {"start": 2022.54, "end": 2026.54, "text": " how blessed we are to get this process, bona fide process,"}, {"start": 2026.54, "end": 2030.54, "text": " get a bona fide spiritual master,"}, {"start": 2030.54, "end": 2033.54, "text": " then definitely we'll follow this process sincerely."}, {"start": 2033.54, "end": 2036.54, "text": " And if we follow this process sincerely,"}, {"start": 2036.54, "end": 2039.54, "text": " our liberation from material existence is guaranteed."}, {"start": 2039.54, "end": 2040.54, "text": " Let's stop here."}, {"start": 2040.54, "end": 2044.54, "text": " Grantharaj Shri Matbhagavatam ki Shri Prabhupada ki"}]}